;Digital Inclusion means supporting universal access to the whole Internet
Digitalno vključevanje pomeni spodbujanje vsesplošnega dostopa do celotnega interneta


;We should all have affordable, high-quality, unrestricted access to the whole Web, so the whole world can benefit.
Vsi bi morali imeti možnost ugodnega, visokokakovostnega in neomejenega dostopa do celotnega interneta, od katerega ima lahko korist cel svet.


;To participate online, you have to be able to get online. Programs have emerged that offer free or subsidized Internet access, but it is often slow or restricted, creating a ‘poor Internet for poor people.’ At its most extreme, governments worldwide are turning off all or parts of the Internet to serve their own agendas, which can threaten human rights and even the health of the global economy.
Če želite sodelovati na spletu, morate biti tam prisotni. Pojavile so se pobude, ki ponujajo brezplačen ali subvencioniran dostop do interneta, vendar je ta pogosto počasen ali omejen, kar ustvarja "reven internet za revne". Vlade po vsem svetu pa v skrajnih primerih celo onemogočijo ves internet ali pa njegove dele, da ta služi njihovim lastnim načrtom, kar lahko ogrozi človekove pravice in celo zdravje svetovnega gospodarstva.


